description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the Dow Jones Transportation Average Index composed of U.S. equities in the transportation sector.
 The fund generally invests at least 90% of its assets in securities of the underlying index and in depositary receipts representing securities of the underlying index. The underlying index measures the performance of large, well-known companies within the transportation sector of the U.S. equity market. The fund is non-diversified.
